org.eel.kitchen.jsonschema.syntax

Class PositiveIntegerSyntaxChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eel.kitchen.jsonschema.syntax.SimpleSyntaxChecker
      • org.eel.kitchen.jsonschema.syntax.PositiveIntegerSyntaxChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SyntaxChecker

    public class PositiveIntegerSyntaxChecker
extends SimpleSyntaxChecker
    Syntax validator for keywords having a positive integer value as an argument

    Note that this is Java, which means there is the limit that such arguments cannot be greater than Integer.MAX_VALUE. While not strictly conformant with the specification, this implementation enforces this.
